## Typography Standards

### Font Families

**Primary (Headings):**
- Recommended: System fonts (-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto)
- Or: [Your brand font]

**Secondary (Body):**
- Recommended: System fonts for readability
- Or: [Your brand font]

### Type Scale

**Recommended modular scale (1.25 ratio):**
- h1: 48px / 3rem
- h2: 39px / 2.441rem
- h3: 31px / 1.953rem
- h4: 25px / 1.563rem
- h5: 20px / 1.25rem
- body: 16px / 1rem
- small: 13px / 0.8rem

### Line Height

- Headings: 1.2 - 1.3
- Body text: 1.5 - 1.7
- Large text (>24px): 1.4

### Font Weights

- Light: 300 (optional, use sparingly)
- Regular: 400 (body text)
- Medium: 500 (emphasis)
- Bold: 700 (headings, strong emphasis)

