## Spacing Standards

### Spacing Scale (8px grid)

- 4px (0.25rem) - Tight spacing
- 8px (0.5rem) - Small spacing
- 12px (0.75rem) - Default gap
- 16px (1rem) - Base unit
- 24px (1.5rem) - Medium spacing
- 32px (2rem) - Large spacing
- 48px (3rem) - XL spacing
- 64px (4rem) - Section spacing
- 96px (6rem) - Major section spacing

### Component Spacing

**Cards:**
- Padding: 24px (desktop), 16px (mobile)
- Gap between cards: 24px

**Buttons:**
- Padding: 12px 24px (medium)
- Padding: 8px 16px (small)
- Padding: 16px 32px (large)

**Sections:**
- Vertical padding: 64px (desktop), 48px (mobile)
- Container max-width: 1200px
- Container padding: 24px (sides)

