## Component Guidelines

### Buttons

**Primary Button:**
- Background: Primary color
- Text: White
- Hover: Darken 10%
- Border radius: 6px (or per brand)
- Font weight: 500-600
- Minimum width: 120px

**Secondary Button:**
- Background: Transparent
- Border: 2px solid primary
- Text: Primary color
- Hover: Background primary (10% opacity)

**Ghost Button:**
- Background: Transparent
- Text: Primary color
- Hover: Subtle background

### Form Inputs

- Border: 1px solid neutral
- Border radius: 6px
- Padding: 12px 16px
- Focus: Primary color border + box-shadow
- Error state: Red border
- Disabled: Gray background, reduced opacity

### Cards

- Background: White
- Border: 1px solid light gray or none
- Border radius: 8px
- Box shadow: Subtle elevation
- Padding: 24px
- Hover: Slight lift (transform + shadow)

