## Animation Guidelines

### Performance

**Use only transform and opacity for animations:**
```css
/* Good - 60fps */
transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;

/* Bad - can cause jank */
transition: width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
```

### Duration

- Micro-interactions: 150-200ms
- Standard transitions: 250-300ms
- Complex animations: 400-500ms
- Never exceed 600ms

### Easing

- Default: ease-in-out
- Entering: ease-out
- Exiting: ease-in
- Bouncy (sparingly): cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55)

